The paper deals with real-time semantic segmentation using convolutional neural networks, which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a novel and efficient module for CNNs, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of real-time semantic segmentation is relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM) fields.
